{"tid":339664,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung Galaxy S8 Active曝光 規格最強的三防手機","createTime":"2017-07-29T08:55:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T09:07:34.000Z","uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ddbc084f47f6a3d647879ec2974f1172692b71c","tid":339664,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:55:30.000Z","msg":"ASUS ZenFone 4 Pro 配備2X變焦雙鏡頭相機模組！<br />\nby LPComment   2017.07.29 07:10AM <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cool3c.com/files/contentparty/lrP38IH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2Fcontentparty%2FlrP38IH.jpg&h=59cf7635&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017-07-29 07:10:47 by 科技暖男 - 劉胖胖 @ LPComment <br />\n<br />\n華碩的下一代手機 ZenFone 4 系列即將推出，不過稍早已經有疑似 ASUS ZenFone 4 Pro 諜照於義大利網站 DDay.it 曝光。照片中疑似 ASUS ZenFone 4 的手機型號為 Z01GS（歐洲型號，台版型號應為 Z01GD），正面採用 2.5D 玻璃與 5.7 吋 QHD（2K） 螢幕，螢幕下方有指紋辨識器。作業系統是 Android 7.1.1。來源表示 ASUS ZenFone 4 Pro 的處理器搭載高通 s835，並配備 6GB RAM 與 64GB ROM，相機部分的規格來不及無法確認（可能是 2100 萬畫素），但可以從照片看到其採用可提供 2 倍變焦效果的雙鏡頭設計，並支援雙補光燈。不過 DDay.it 也指出，他們拍到的這支 ASUS ZenFone 4 Pro 有套著一層保護套（看起來像是在某種非公開的場地，例如零組件供應商的閉門展示），因此目前還不確定機身外型的實際樣貌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cool3c.com/files/contentparty/ETjTbTi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2Fcontentparty%2FETjTbTi.jpg&h=68f2e934&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cool3c.com/files/contentparty/P9O9n60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2Fcontentparty%2FP9O9n60.jpg&h=fa2ed783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/127222\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F127222&d=gcO4znxt49ZZR8l1uLQ8lzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=aceb973c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/127222</a><br />\n癮科技facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cool3c.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcool3c.tw&d=gcO4znxt49ZZR8l1uLQ8lzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c6e2c5a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cool3c.tw</a><br />\n<br />\nZenFone 4:<br />\n<br />\n- 2.5D 玻璃<br />\n<br />\n- 5.7 吋 2K 螢幕<br />\n<br />\n- 指紋辨識器<br />\n<br />\n- 雙鏡頭<br />\n<br />\n- Android 7.1.1<br />\n<br />\n- Qualcomm Snapdragon 835<br />\n<br />\n- 6GB RAM<br />\n<br />\n- 64GB ROM"},{"pid":"c25ffb1493e57bf4864298b2c54f43da2bd949eb","tid":339664,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:56:37.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n文不對題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再貼過"},{"pid":"a0fd01b9a623d2b47b09192dfea676cdc831856f","tid":339664,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T09:07:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<br />\n文不對題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再貼過</blockquote>你講多一次"}]}